snippet.textDisplay: It takes at least three months to figure out an anti-virus or a shot that will help. In this case people are contagious during incubation and shortly after they are cured by their own antibodies. What's more this looks like something China accidentally let loose and then blamed it on the wet markets because they need to stop those anyway
